{"tid":526271,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【涉偷拍裙底案提堂　休班警不獲法援需另聘律師】","createTime":"2018-01-11T13:06:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-12T00:51:39.000Z","uid":5195,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"6a5ea4452b6c952eb70445cb10b5da1d4feeea65","tid":526271,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T13:06:43.000Z","msg":"一名案發時隸屬水警西分區巡邏小隊的休班警員，涉嫌去年1月21日在旺角港鐵站的扶手電梯，偷拍一名女子裙底，被控一項作出有違公德的行為罪，案件今日（1月11日）在西九龍裁判法院提堂，被告毋須答辯，案件押後至3月8日再訊。<br />\n<br />\n辯方律師今日申請將案件押後8星期，以索取文件之餘，並指其資產入息超過當值律師服務的限額，需時尋找私人律師，裁判官批准申請，被告獲准以原有條件保釋"},{"pid":"8ff393584847ba88b26b299c94848191ce6ca187","tid":526271,"uid":50214,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T13:13:47.000Z","msg":"警...檢。"},{"pid":"5df8883ba85ba17730f058bb0e3d9bceedb2cce7","tid":526271,"uid":33896,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"8ff393584847ba88b26b299c94848191ce6ca187","tid":526271,"uid":50214,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T13:13:47.000Z","msg":"警...檢。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T13:15:18.000Z","msg":"警理呀"},{"pid":"f2f0f5e07eddf13dc3b2a9bc9e562322c18bb9ea","tid":526271,"uid":134323,"like":12,"dislike":2,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T13:18:30.000Z","msg":"阿 sir 影裙底唔洗你教！"},{"pid":"f40c439e06a042875886df25e2bf4a64f2511c1f","tid":526271,"uid":22554,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T13:19:55.000Z","msg":"點解唔開名, 平時D 普通人唔係實開名?"},{"pid":"3087ada19a07832aa74180289aebf57a93ea0442","tid":526271,"uid":25794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T13:21:15.000Z","msg":"抵撚死"},{"pid":"cbe960b949948fa20a7f67f818a085fb3b873420","tid":526271,"uid":5195,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T13:50:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5ce19f334b8fd7684aa04125b63b20ef288ec3a","tid":526271,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20